//  5th: 32-bit unsigned integer representing bits  0 to  31 of FOLLOW set
//  6th: 32-bit unsigned integer representing bits 32 to  63 of FOLLOW set
//  7th: 32-bit unsigned integer representing bits 64 to  95 of FOLLOW set


